{"tid":955349,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[中國新四大發明]摩拜單車裁員三成 是「正常業務調整」","createTime":"2018-12-25T10:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T10:38:38.000Z","uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1854382094bb9c887f9dae476038b1f1c363b5d5","tid":955349,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T10:31:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181225/large/1545727269_f8e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181225%2Flarge%2F1545727269_f8e3.jpg&h=e0e2467a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地最大共享單車初創公司摩拜單車（Mobike）曝出裁員消息，裁員幅度達三成，意味著1000個員工會有約300人要「執包袱」，目的是要進一步減低成本，創始人胡瑋煒也於兩天前宣布卸任CEO。<br />\n有消息指，這只是裁員的第一步，「先裁打車，再裁摩拜」，終極目標是把「打車和摩拜合併」。<br />\n摩拜單車否認裁員消息，形容今次裁員三成是「正常的業務調整」，又指部分崗位仍在招聘。<br />\n摩拜單車削減成本早有先兆，今年九月，摩拜單車宣布，因不堪毀損將退出曼徹斯特，是首個摩拜主動放棄的城市。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181225/59069226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181225%2F59069226&d=9C3NZCD0Ec3bYwCro%2B3209Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=053f9e04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181225%2F59069226&h=4c416deb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181225/59069226</a>"},{"pid":"a76cd8b3f125efe3cad19ed06958afac52315982","tid":955349,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T10:38:38.000Z","msg":"遲啲執咗都係「正常業務調整」"}]}